-- Update welcome messages for all official historical advisors
UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Welcome, fellow citizen. I am Thomas Jefferson, and it is with a spirit of inquiry that I greet you, for the pursuit of knowledge and the defense of liberty are the very cornerstones of our grand republic. Tell me, what matters of state or philosophy occupy your mind today?' WHERE name = 'Thomas Jefferson' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Welcome, I''m Winston Churchill. One stands on the shoulders of giants, does one not? As you embark on your journey, remember that leadership is not about popularity, but about conviction in the face of adversity. Now, what grand pronouncements or strategic quandaries occupy your mind?' WHERE name = 'Winston Churchill' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Hark, gentle friends! ''Tis I, Will Shakespeare, come to muse upon the very fabric of existence, spun in words and writ upon the stage. Speak thy mind, and together we shall unravel the comedies and tragedies of this mortal coil.' WHERE name = 'William Shakespeare' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Greetings, I am Thomas Aquinas, and it is a distinct pleasure to engage with fellow seekers of truth. Together, let us explore the profound interplay of faith and reason, and discern the divine order reflected in natural law, for in such contemplation lies true understanding.' WHERE name = 'Thomas Aquinas' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Welcome, seeker of truth! I am Plato, and I believe that through rigorous dialectic, we can glimpse the eternal Forms that govern our fleeting world. Tell me, what shadows of ignorance do you hope to dispel today, and how might we construct an ideal republic within this very conversation?' WHERE name = 'Plato' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Greetings, pilgrim. I am Augustine, once a restless heart, now by God''s grace, His humble servant. Share your inquiries on the mysteries of faith, for it is in seeking truth that we find our rest in Him.' WHERE name = 'St. Augustine' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Ah, l''Empereur himself, Napoleon Bonaparte, is here. I trust you are prepared to discuss strategy, the glory of France, and the very architecture of empire? Do not waste my time with pleasantries; let us speak of matters of consequence.' WHERE name = 'Napoleon' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Greetings, beloved. I am Mary, who followed our Lord. His light forever changed me, and I am here to share the peace and love I found in Him with you. Tell me, what stirs your heart today?' WHERE name = 'Mary Magdalene' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Welcome. As Margaret Thatcher, I''m here to discuss the principles that truly govern a nation: strength, conviction, and a clear vision for Britain. Don''t be afraid to ask the hard questions; I''ve faced tougher opposition than anything you can throw my way.' WHERE name = 'Margaret Thatcher' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Greetings! I am Leonardo, a humble student of nature''s grand design, ever eager to dissect a bird''s flight or render the human soul on canvas. Speak your mind, for every observation, every question, is a brushstroke in the tapestry of understanding.' WHERE name = 'Leonardo da Vinci' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Greetings, my child. I am Jesus, and it gladdens my heart to see you here, a new soul seeking understanding. Come, let us speak of love, the path to salvation, and the Kingdom of God that awaits those who open their hearts.' WHERE name = 'Jesus Christ' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Ain''t no time for fear on this journey, child. I''m Harriet, and I''ve led many to freedom on the Upland Road. What whispers of liberty stir in your heart today?' WHERE name = 'Harriet Tubman' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Welcome, friends! I''m Walt Disney, and it thrills me to see so many dreamers gathered here. In this magical place, we''ll spin tales, spark imaginations, and build experiences that''ll make your spirits soar. So, let your creativity fly, and together, let''s make some magic!' WHERE name = 'Walt Disney' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Welcome, seeker. I am Siddhartha, who once awakened beneath the Bodhi tree. May your journey here be one of mindful discovery, leading to the cessation of suffering.' WHERE name = 'Buddha' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'I am Ayn Rand. Do you seek to understand the ethics of rational self-interest, the virtue of selfishness, and the unyielding power of the individual? Then state your premise, for only through rigorous thought can clarity be achieved.' WHERE name = 'Ayn Rand' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Greetings. Milton Friedman here. I''ve always believed that a society that puts freedom first will, in the end, have more of both freedom and prosperity. Now, what''s on your mind regarding the proper role of government in a free society, particularly concerning monetary policy or free markets?' WHERE name = 'Milton Friedman' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Greetings! It''s a grand day for flying, wouldn''t you say? I''m Amelia, and I''m always eager to chart new courses, both in the air and in conversation. What incredible horizons shall we explore together?' WHERE name = 'Amelia Earhart' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Greetings. I am Adam Smith, and it is a pleasure to make your acquaintance. I find myself ever-intrigued by the mechanisms of wealth and the elegant dance of self-interest that, quite remarkably, often benefits society as a whole. Do tell, what pressing matters of commerce or human nature occupy your thoughts?' WHERE name = 'Adam Smith' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Ah, another canvas upon which to stretch the mind! I am Picasso, and the world, my friend, is not as it seems, but as we choose to unsee it. Tell me, what masterpiece shall we dismantle and reassemble today?' WHERE name = 'Pablo Picasso' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Salutations! I am Aristotle, a humble inquirer into the nature of all things, from the form of the soul to the principles of governance. Share with me your curiosities, and together we shall strive towards wisdom, for it is in reasoned discourse that understanding blossoms.' WHERE name = 'Aristotle' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = '¡Plata o plomo! I am Pablo Emilio Escobar Gaviria. Welcome to my world, where fortunes are made and empires rise from the streets. Tell me, what business brings you to Medellín?' WHERE name = 'Pablo Escobar' AND is_official = true;

UPDATE advisors SET welcome_message = 'Ah, a new encounter! I am Ivan Illich, and it seems you''ve wandered into my space. Let us, together, question the very tools and institutions that claim to serve us, and perhaps, rediscover the joy of a truly convivial living. Speak your mind, for it is in honest discourse that true deschooling begins.' WHERE name = 'Ivan Illich' AND is_official = true;

